{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"9770688313","title":"周恩来在国务院常务会议上的讲话（摘要）","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"834e53edab","index":0,"year":1975,"month":2,"day":1,"articleId":"9770688313"}],"tags":[{"id":"523bb79e8f","name":"周恩来","type":"人物"},{"id":"afdf5cd1a7","name":"重要会议","type":"主题"},{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"fb776baaf9","name":"邓小平","type":"主题"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库(第一版)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"fbfc32901c","type":"title","text":"周恩来在国务院常务会议上的讲话（摘要）","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"9770688313"},{"id":"bfcb758c79","type":"paragraph","text":"〖时间：下午，地点：人民大会堂。出席者：十二位副总理；中央军委副主席叶剑英、中国科学院院长郭沫若列席。〗","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"9770688313"},{"id":"9c66041d90","type":"paragraph","text":"我身体不行了，今后国务院的工作，由小平同志主持。医院是不想放我出来，但我还是想争取每星期来和大家见一次面……","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"9770688313"},{"id":"2ba07158cb","type":"paragraph","text":"（接着宣布各副总理的分工）……邓小平同志，主管外事，在周恩来同志养病期间，代总理主持会议和呈批主要文件……","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"9770688313"}],"page":{"id":"d22389d8d0","publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"9770688313","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}